snippet.title: Coromon - Official Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to embark on an adventure across the Velua region, collect creatures, and save the world when the monster taming game, Coromon, launches on Nintendo Switch, PC, and Mac on March 31, 2022.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #Coromon
